1202
01:22:49,079 --> 01:22:51,380
[SPEAKER_01] basic trust, osnovno povjerenje,

1203
01:22:52,340 --> 01:22:55,319
[SPEAKER_01] da djete prima ljubav

1204
01:22:55,319 --> 01:22:57,380
[SPEAKER_01] isključivo kroz pažnju,

1205
01:22:57,380 --> 01:22:58,520
[SPEAKER_01] nježnost, dodir,

1206
01:22:58,520 --> 01:22:59,560
[SPEAKER_01] fizički dodir,

1207
01:22:59,560 --> 01:23:00,500
[SPEAKER_01] neko škakranje,

1208
01:23:00,500 --> 01:23:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] provođenje vremena s njim

1209
01:23:01,960 --> 01:23:03,399
[SPEAKER_01] i tek tada može ući

1210
01:23:03,399 --> 01:23:05,800
[SPEAKER_01] u drugu fazu psihološkog razvoja,

1211
01:23:05,800 --> 01:23:07,300
[SPEAKER_01] a to je negacijska faza.

1212
01:23:07,300 --> 01:23:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] To nekad djete s dvije godine

1213
01:23:08,960 --> 01:23:09,859
[SPEAKER_01] sjećate se,

1214
01:23:09,859 --> 01:23:11,020
[SPEAKER_01] spremno reći ne.

1215
01:23:11,020 --> 01:23:12,140
[SPEAKER_01] O, da.

1216
01:23:12,140 --> 01:23:12,859
[SPEAKER_01] Govori ne.

1217
01:23:12,859 --> 01:23:13,859
[SPEAKER_01] I baš da ti se po povodu.

1218
01:23:13,859 --> 01:23:15,520
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je li je taj primilo

1219
01:23:15,520 --> 01:23:16,260
[SPEAKER_01] dovoljno ljubavi

1220
01:23:16,260 --> 01:23:17,100
[SPEAKER_01] da shvati da je ona

1221
01:23:17,100 --> 01:23:18,359
[SPEAKER_01] druga osoba,

1222
01:23:18,359 --> 01:23:19,899
[SPEAKER_01] ona nije mi mama ni tata

1223
01:23:19,899 --> 01:23:21,640
[SPEAKER_01] i može i tad govori ne

1224
01:23:21,640 --> 01:23:22,560
[SPEAKER_01] i kad želi nešto,

1225
01:23:22,560 --> 01:23:23,739
[SPEAKER_01] samo zato da dokaže.

1226
01:23:23,739 --> 01:23:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] I sad uzmite obzir

1227
01:23:25,079 --> 01:23:27,920
[SPEAKER_01] koliko djece odrasta

1228
01:23:27,920 --> 01:23:29,720
[SPEAKER_01] bez da je primilo tu ljubav

1229
01:23:29,720 --> 01:23:31,380
[SPEAKER_01] i nikad ne zna ureći ne.

1230
01:23:31,380 --> 01:23:33,220
[SPEAKER_01] Pogotovo u radu s djevojkama,

1231
01:23:33,220 --> 01:23:34,739
[SPEAKER_01] malo da i to spomenemo,

1232
01:23:34,739 --> 01:23:37,520
[SPEAKER_01] djevojke koje ulaze u

1233
01:23:37,520 --> 01:23:39,300
[SPEAKER_01] teške situacije

1234
01:23:39,300 --> 01:23:41,399
[SPEAKER_01] koje počinju davat svoje tijelo

1235
01:23:41,399 --> 01:23:44,079
[SPEAKER_01] da bi zapravo kupile ljubav,

1236
01:23:44,079 --> 01:23:45,399
[SPEAKER_01] što one čine?

1237
01:23:45,399 --> 01:23:47,140
[SPEAKER_01] Oni ne zna ureći ne

1238
01:23:47,140 --> 01:23:49,560
[SPEAKER_01] zato jer nisu prošli

1239
01:23:49,560 --> 01:23:50,520
[SPEAKER_01] na tu prvu fazu.

1240
01:23:50,520 --> 01:23:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] On je čezno za tom ljubavni

1241
01:23:52,800 --> 01:23:55,699
[SPEAKER_01] i misle da će dobiti

1242
01:23:55,699 --> 01:23:57,039
[SPEAKER_01] kroz nekog muškarca,

1243
01:23:57,039 --> 01:23:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] često i starijeg koji ih iskoristi

1244
01:23:58,960 --> 01:23:59,720
[SPEAKER_01] na taj način,

1245
01:23:59,720 --> 01:24:01,199
[SPEAKER_01] oni kratko trenut to dobiju,

1246
01:24:01,199 --> 01:24:02,359
[SPEAKER_01] koji poslije ih odbaci

1247
01:24:02,359 --> 01:24:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] i oni tako ulaze u začarani krug,

1248
01:24:04,539 --> 01:24:06,739
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo gdje se razočaranje

1249
01:24:06,739 --> 01:24:08,199
[SPEAKER_01] gomila u njihovu životu.

1250
01:24:08,199 --> 01:24:09,140
[SPEAKER_01] To je isto primjer,

1251
01:24:09,140 --> 01:24:11,319
[SPEAKER_01] najčešće da se to dogodilo

1252
01:24:11,319 --> 01:24:13,159
[SPEAKER_01] zbog očeva koji su zakazali.

1253
01:24:13,600 --> 01:24:15,060
[SPEAKER_01] Zato ja nastujem svojeg čerkici

1254
01:24:15,060 --> 01:24:17,560
[SPEAKER_01] da što više ljubavi potvrde,

1255
01:24:17,560 --> 01:24:19,020
[SPEAKER_01] ali biti dosljedano

1256
01:24:19,020 --> 01:24:20,340
[SPEAKER_01] oko onog što smo rekli ne,

1257
01:24:20,340 --> 01:24:21,699
[SPEAKER_01] onda je to stvarno ne

1258
01:24:21,699 --> 01:24:23,520
[SPEAKER_01] i pazimo da smo mama i ja tu,

1259
01:24:23,520 --> 01:24:25,060
[SPEAKER_01] znači moja žena i ja,

1260
01:24:25,060 --> 01:24:27,039
[SPEAKER_01] da smo usuglašeni.

1261
01:24:27,039 --> 01:24:28,720
[SPEAKER_01] I ravnobrani partnere.

1262
01:24:28,720 --> 01:24:29,340
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1263
01:24:29,340 --> 01:24:30,359
[SPEAKER_01] I da nema sad,

1264
01:24:30,359 --> 01:24:31,880
[SPEAKER_01] ok, tata nije pusti,

1265
01:24:31,880 --> 01:24:33,319
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću mamu sa strane to piti,

1266
01:24:33,319 --> 01:24:34,439
[SPEAKER_01] pa će mi ona dati.

1267
01:24:34,859 --> 01:24:36,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što je jako važno,

1268
01:24:36,039 --> 01:24:39,119
[SPEAKER_01] da druša mladjeca su još mala,

1269
01:24:39,119 --> 01:24:42,439
[SPEAKER_01] ali imam iskustva rada sa ljudima,

1270
01:24:42,439 --> 01:24:43,939
[SPEAKER_01] sa mladima što je jako važno,

1271
01:24:43,939 --> 01:24:47,140
[SPEAKER_01] nije dobro da majka kritizira

1272
01:24:47,140 --> 01:24:48,859
[SPEAKER_01] otca pred djetetom i obrnuto,

1273
01:24:48,859 --> 01:24:50,199
[SPEAKER_01] da otac kritizira majku,

1274
01:24:50,199 --> 01:24:51,199
[SPEAKER_01] govori protiv nje.

1275
01:24:51,199 --> 01:24:52,779
[SPEAKER_01] Znači oni moraju biti usklađeni.

1276
01:24:52,779 --> 01:24:54,100
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno da se mogu nekad

1277
01:24:54,100 --> 01:24:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] poslađati pred djetetom,

1278
01:24:55,260 --> 01:24:56,439
[SPEAKER_01] jer djete treba odrastati

1279
01:24:56,439 --> 01:24:57,260
[SPEAKER_01] u nekoj normalnoj.

1280
01:24:57,260 --> 01:24:58,600
[SPEAKER_01] A nekoj staklenim zvonom.

1281
01:24:58,600 --> 01:25:00,100
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, da se to pokaže,

1282
01:25:00,100 --> 01:25:01,399
[SPEAKER_01] ali bitno je isto tako

1283
01:25:01,399 --> 01:25:03,479
[SPEAKER_01] da se vidi taj sklad

1284
01:25:03,479 --> 01:25:05,119
[SPEAKER_01] bračnog pare,

1285
01:25:05,119 --> 01:25:06,140
[SPEAKER_01] koji njima stvara

1286
01:25:06,140 --> 01:25:08,020
[SPEAKER_01] osjećaj njija,

1287
01:25:08,020 --> 01:25:10,159
[SPEAKER_01] kreativnosti

1288
01:25:10,159 --> 01:25:11,260
[SPEAKER_01] i mogućnosti

1289
01:25:11,260 --> 01:25:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] da razvijaju svoje talente.

1290
01:25:12,539 --> 01:25:15,359
[SPEAKER_01] Pošto je moj posao takav,

1291
01:25:15,359 --> 01:25:16,340
[SPEAKER_01] slično kao i Antin,

1292
01:25:16,340 --> 01:25:17,680
[SPEAKER_01] da sam stalno na potu

1293
01:25:17,680 --> 01:25:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] sa moja cvita,

1294
01:25:18,619 --> 01:25:19,600
[SPEAKER_01] znači prvo djete,

1295
01:25:19,600 --> 01:25:21,300
[SPEAKER_01] ona nema di nije bila.

1296
01:25:21,300 --> 01:25:23,359
[SPEAKER_01] Samo u Travniku je bila pet pust,

1297
01:25:23,359 --> 01:25:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] a badja Luci, devet.

1298
01:25:26,180 --> 01:25:27,979
[SPEAKER_01] po svuda je išla s nama

1299
01:25:27,979 --> 01:25:30,239
[SPEAKER_01] i mislim da je tu isto

1300
01:25:30,239 --> 01:25:32,220
[SPEAKER_01] štjecala i jednu širinu

1301
01:25:32,220 --> 01:25:33,220
[SPEAKER_01] koja se kasnije vidila

1302
01:25:33,220 --> 01:25:34,600
[SPEAKER_01] i u vrtiću.

1303
01:25:34,600 --> 01:25:36,140
[SPEAKER_01] Sa malim smo isto nastavili,

1304
01:25:36,140 --> 01:25:37,659
[SPEAKER_01] što česte sad stroje vidjet ćemo.

1305
01:25:37,659 --> 01:25:40,020
[SPEAKER_00] Treće je na putu.

1306
01:25:40,020 --> 01:25:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] Treće je već na putu.

1307
01:25:41,960 --> 01:25:42,659
[SPEAKER_00] Evo da budemo,

1308
01:25:42,659 --> 01:25:44,079
[SPEAKER_00] da kada cvita je na putu

1309
01:25:44,079 --> 01:25:44,939
[SPEAKER_00] od rođenja,

1310
01:25:44,939 --> 01:25:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] a treće je sada na putu.

1311
01:25:46,079 --> 01:25:48,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ali čisto malo da razbijemo.

1312
01:25:48,479 --> 01:25:49,300
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ste rekli,

1313
01:25:49,300 --> 01:25:50,140
[SPEAKER_00] ono s dvije godine

1314
01:25:50,140 --> 01:25:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] nam počinju govoriti

1315
01:25:51,380 --> 01:25:53,340
[SPEAKER_00] ne, ne treje to kratko,

1316
01:25:53,340 --> 01:25:54,680
[SPEAKER_00] to traje, znate.

1317
01:25:54,680 --> 01:25:56,159
[SPEAKER_00] Traje, traje.

1318
01:25:56,159 --> 01:25:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je stvarno i vlastite volje.

1319
01:25:58,000 --> 01:26:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] To traje, to traje prilično.

1320
01:26:00,039 --> 01:26:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] To ćete obojca vidjeti,

1321
01:26:01,460 --> 01:26:03,220
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo s tinejdžerskim godinama.

1322
01:26:03,220 --> 01:26:04,659
[SPEAKER_00] To doista traje.

1323
01:26:04,659 --> 01:26:05,859
[SPEAKER_00] I to treba izdržati.

1324
01:26:05,859 --> 01:26:07,020
[SPEAKER_02] Mogu ja ponuditi samo jednu,

1325
01:26:07,020 --> 01:26:08,920
[SPEAKER_02] naravnu sliku za ljude,

1326
01:26:08,920 --> 01:26:10,159
[SPEAKER_02] da im je to lakše razumijeti.

1327
01:26:10,159 --> 01:26:13,840
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, izgranja osobnosti ljudske

1328
01:26:13,840 --> 01:26:15,020
[SPEAKER_02] i onoga onda,

1329
01:26:15,020 --> 01:26:18,000
[SPEAKER_02] ti nekih temeljnih vrijednosti,

1330
01:26:18,000 --> 01:26:18,779
[SPEAKER_02] ti temeljnih stvari

1331
01:26:18,779 --> 01:26:19,920
[SPEAKER_02] koje ja imam u svom srcu,

1332
01:26:19,920 --> 01:26:21,500
[SPEAKER_02] na temelju kojih ja živim.

1333
01:26:21,920 --> 01:26:23,779
[SPEAKER_02] I to puno toga ide na nesvjesnoj razini.

1334
01:26:23,779 --> 01:26:26,800
[SPEAKER_02] To je isto ko kad gradiš zgradu.

1335
01:26:26,800 --> 01:26:29,739
[SPEAKER_02] Ako ne napraviš dobro temelje,

1336
01:26:29,739 --> 01:26:31,720
[SPEAKER_02] možete napraviti najbolju,

1337
01:26:31,720 --> 01:26:33,260
[SPEAKER_02] gori strukturu moguću

1338
01:26:33,260 --> 01:26:34,579
[SPEAKER_02] i možeš ju savršavati

1339
01:26:34,579 --> 01:26:36,520
[SPEAKER_02] i raditi iznutra najbolje stvari.

1340
01:26:36,899 --> 01:26:38,239
[SPEAKER_02] Ali ako temelji nisu dobri,

1341
01:26:38,239 --> 01:26:39,979
[SPEAKER_02] ta zgrada cijela može pasti.

1342
01:26:39,979 --> 01:26:42,680
[SPEAKER_02] Da onda su ključne su te temeljne stvari.

1343
01:26:42,680 --> 01:26:44,239
[SPEAKER_02] Sad mi žijemo u vremenu

1344
01:26:44,239 --> 01:26:46,460
[SPEAKER_02] gdje se ljudi nisu sposobni

1345
01:26:46,460 --> 01:26:47,859
[SPEAKER_02] za razumjeti svoje uloge

1346
01:26:47,859 --> 01:26:49,840
[SPEAKER_02] i za razumjeti što je djeci potrebno

1347
01:26:49,840 --> 01:26:51,979
[SPEAKER_02] i onda te temeljne stvari su najugroženije.

1348
01:26:51,979 --> 01:26:54,560
[SPEAKER_02] Većina brakova kad se raspada,

1349
01:26:54,560 --> 01:26:56,699
[SPEAKER_02] raspada se u prvoj, drujoj, trećoj godini braka.

1350
01:26:56,699 --> 01:26:58,760
[SPEAKER_02] Najčešće dođe do začelića,

1351
01:26:58,760 --> 01:27:00,020
[SPEAKER_02] do djece, već se stvori.

1352
01:27:00,020 --> 01:27:01,979
[SPEAKER_02] I sad tamo gdje si ti grad doću

1353
01:27:01,979 --> 01:27:03,960
[SPEAKER_02] o azu, sigurnosti, ljubavi i sve,

1354
01:27:06,899 --> 01:27:07,960
[SPEAKER_02] stvari su u neredu.

1355
01:27:07,960 --> 01:27:09,979
[SPEAKER_02] Rekao sam ovo prije da je temeljnast rana,

1356
01:27:09,979 --> 01:27:11,319
[SPEAKER_02] rana odbačenosti,

1357
01:27:11,319 --> 01:27:13,760
[SPEAKER_02] koja je ono brutalno, brutalno

1358
01:27:13,760 --> 01:27:15,880
[SPEAKER_02] ovoga dijeluje u posvesti čovjeka

1359
01:27:15,880 --> 01:27:17,359
[SPEAKER_02] i poslije čovjeka do odrasta

1360
01:27:17,359 --> 01:27:19,079
[SPEAKER_02] on vjeruje, ja ne vrijedim.

1361
01:27:19,079 --> 01:27:21,279
[SPEAKER_02] On čuje doslovno kod da ta laž

1362
01:27:21,279 --> 01:27:23,079
[SPEAKER_02] diktira njegovim osjećajima

1363
01:27:23,079 --> 01:27:25,159
[SPEAKER_02] i ponašanjem, ja ne vrijedim.

1364
01:27:25,159 --> 01:27:27,079
[SPEAKER_02] On toga čak, nekak puno ljudi

1365
01:27:27,079 --> 01:27:28,760
[SPEAKER_02] nisu ne svjesni da ta rana dijela

1366
01:27:28,760 --> 01:27:30,100
[SPEAKER_02] u njihovom životu, ja ne vrijedim.

1367
01:27:30,100 --> 01:27:32,220
[SPEAKER_02] I onda čak sabotiraju sami sebe

1368
01:27:32,220 --> 01:27:33,279
[SPEAKER_02] i kad treba ući u blagost,

1369
01:27:33,340 --> 01:27:35,439
[SPEAKER_02] kad treba ući u dožit polet,

1370
01:27:35,439 --> 01:27:38,340
[SPEAKER_02] obori ih njihova uvjerenja

1371
01:27:38,340 --> 01:27:39,260
[SPEAKER_02] o njihovoj vrijednost.

1372
01:27:39,260 --> 01:27:41,420
[SPEAKER_02] Dao da bih rekao da su ključne stvari

1373
01:27:41,420 --> 01:27:42,180
[SPEAKER_02] za naše društvo,

1374
01:27:42,180 --> 01:27:44,680
[SPEAKER_02] da te temelne stvari se dobro sagrade.

1375
01:27:44,680 --> 01:27:46,479
[SPEAKER_02] Zato da, ono jednostavno,

1376
01:27:46,479 --> 01:27:47,859
[SPEAKER_02] za naša obitelj, naša djeca,

1377
01:27:47,859 --> 01:27:50,880
[SPEAKER_02] ključne stvari, pogotovo za malo djecu,

1378
01:27:50,880 --> 01:27:53,420
[SPEAKER_02] sad ću to reći u tri najjednostanije rečenice.

1379
01:27:53,420 --> 01:27:55,439
[SPEAKER_02] Prvo, ja te želim,

1380
01:27:55,439 --> 01:27:56,500
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam te želio.

1381
01:27:56,500 --> 01:27:58,640
[SPEAKER_02] Koliko ljudi ne želi svoju djecu

1382
01:27:58,640 --> 01:28:00,380
[SPEAKER_02] ili misle druga, treća da je viška,

1383
01:28:00,380 --> 01:28:01,380
[SPEAKER_02] četvrta, onda djete.

1384
01:28:03,340 --> 01:28:07,939
[SPEAKER_02] da je krivo, što se običe rodilo.

1385
01:28:07,939 --> 01:28:10,300
[SPEAKER_02] Najvjerojatno ste prenatalne rane,

1386
01:28:10,300 --> 01:28:11,560
[SPEAKER_02] već utrobi koje nastaju.

1387
01:28:11,560 --> 01:28:12,359
[SPEAKER_02] To je psihologija,

1388
01:28:12,359 --> 01:28:14,359
[SPEAKER_02] je nevovisno o religiji dokazala.

1389
01:28:14,359 --> 01:28:16,420
[SPEAKER_02] Prvo, ti si željen.

1390
01:28:16,420 --> 01:28:19,100
[SPEAKER_02] I svakom od nas to želi biti željen.

1391
01:28:19,100 --> 01:28:20,579
[SPEAKER_02] A ona je voljen, ovo što vam rekao.

1392
01:28:20,579 --> 01:28:23,140
[SPEAKER_02] Onda da ti otraca i majka da ti kaže,

1393
01:28:23,140 --> 01:28:23,779
[SPEAKER_02] ja te vidim.

1394
01:28:23,779 --> 01:28:27,180
[SPEAKER_02] Vidim te, volim te, vidim te, vidim ko si.

1395
01:28:27,180 --> 01:28:28,899
[SPEAKER_02] I onda da te potvrđu,

1396
01:28:28,899 --> 01:28:29,960
[SPEAKER_02] ti si dobar.

1397
01:28:29,960 --> 01:28:32,560
[SPEAKER_02] To što ti imaš u sebi je dobro.

1398
01:28:33,060 --> 01:28:35,180
[SPEAKER_02] i onda ulagati u to, zaljevati to.

1399
01:28:35,180 --> 01:28:36,579
[SPEAKER_02] Izradiš dobre temelje

1400
01:28:36,579 --> 01:28:38,239
[SPEAKER_02] i onda samo lako je zidla,

1401
01:28:38,239 --> 01:28:39,600
[SPEAKER_02] li govore kad su temelji zdravi.

1402
01:28:39,600 --> 01:28:40,800
[SPEAKER_02] Ali kad temelji nisu zdravi,

1403
01:28:40,800 --> 01:28:41,939
[SPEAKER_02] onda je to veliki problem.

1404
01:28:41,939 --> 01:28:44,520
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da, mi kad radimo sad s mladima,

1405
01:28:44,520 --> 01:28:45,420
[SPEAKER_02] mladima obiteljima,

1406
01:28:45,420 --> 01:28:46,800
[SPEAKER_02] inače, ja bih rekao da mi živimo

1407
01:28:46,800 --> 01:28:47,739
[SPEAKER_02] u jednoj subkulturi,

1408
01:28:47,739 --> 01:28:49,579
[SPEAKER_02] s obzirom današnje breme,

1409
01:28:49,579 --> 01:28:50,439
[SPEAKER_02] u našim krugojima,

1410
01:28:50,439 --> 01:28:53,020
[SPEAKER_02] znači, u krugoj naše zajednice,

1411
01:28:53,020 --> 01:28:54,199
[SPEAKER_02] proidašlo oko, ja mislim,

1412
01:28:54,260 --> 01:28:56,100
[SPEAKER_02] 50-ak, 60 brakova.

1413
01:28:56,100 --> 01:28:57,760
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim da je,

1414
01:28:57,760 --> 01:28:59,659
[SPEAKER_02] ako se,

1415
01:28:59,659 --> 01:29:03,220
[SPEAKER_02] u našoj zajednici niko nije rastavio.

1416
01:29:03,220 --> 01:29:04,699
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, mi smo to dalo

1417
01:29:04,699 --> 01:29:05,659
[SPEAKER_02] kontra statistike.

1418
01:29:05,659 --> 01:29:08,000
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, u statistici ide prema svakom drugom,

1419
01:29:08,000 --> 01:29:10,720
[SPEAKER_02] u našoj zajednici niko nije rastavio.

1420
01:29:11,239 --> 01:29:13,180
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, mi imamo nešto što uspjeva.

1421
01:29:13,180 --> 01:29:15,220
[SPEAKER_02] Sada, neko je pametan i poštani

1422
01:29:15,220 --> 01:29:16,199
[SPEAKER_02] da kaže, što vi imate,

1423
01:29:16,199 --> 01:29:17,579
[SPEAKER_02] a zašto vam uspjevaju?

1424
01:29:17,579 --> 01:29:18,760
[SPEAKER_00] Za to, samo si zvala.

1425
01:29:18,760 --> 01:29:21,640
[SPEAKER_00] Imate nešto što pokazuje rezultate.

1426
01:29:21,640 --> 01:29:23,359
[SPEAKER_02] Onda, ja mislim da je došlo

1427
01:29:23,359 --> 01:29:24,479
[SPEAKER_02] do jedne ili dvije rastave

1428
01:29:24,479 --> 01:29:26,000
[SPEAKER_02] onih koji su otišli iz zajednice

1429
01:29:26,000 --> 01:29:28,439
[SPEAKER_02] i zbog stjecanja oko preselili se

1430
01:29:28,439 --> 01:29:29,800
[SPEAKER_02] ili jednostavno živog joga,

1431
01:29:29,800 --> 01:29:32,140
[SPEAKER_02] od njih još hrpe koji su otišli,

1432
01:29:32,140 --> 01:29:34,439
[SPEAKER_02] samo jedan ili dva braka su se rastavila

1433
01:29:34,439 --> 01:29:35,500
[SPEAKER_02] i to je stvarno, ono,

1434
01:29:35,500 --> 01:29:37,220
[SPEAKER_02] za nas, jako bolno i teško.

1435
01:29:41,239 --> 01:29:43,000
[SPEAKER_02] odnosa, obnove uloga

1436
01:29:43,000 --> 01:29:45,239
[SPEAKER_02] i inače, ja imam snažnu ženu.

1437
01:29:45,239 --> 01:29:48,000
[SPEAKER_02] Moja žena je, ono, baš snažna.

1438
01:29:48,000 --> 01:29:49,899
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, ja i ona se hrvamo,

1439
01:29:49,899 --> 01:29:51,159
[SPEAKER_02] mi smo, ono, nema tu.

1440
01:29:51,159 --> 01:29:53,479
[SPEAKER_02] I meni je drago da je moja žena jaka.

1441
01:29:53,479 --> 01:29:55,760
[SPEAKER_02] I moja djeca profitiraju

1442
01:29:55,760 --> 01:29:57,479
[SPEAKER_02] ako imaju jakog tato i jaku mamu.

1443
01:29:57,479 --> 01:29:59,859
[SPEAKER_02] Ne slabu mamu ili slabog tato.

1444
01:29:59,859 --> 01:30:01,199
[SPEAKER_02] Jedno i drugo, moramo biti

1445
01:30:01,199 --> 01:30:03,859
[SPEAKER_02] jaki, snažni, autentični i zdravi

1446
01:30:03,859 --> 01:30:04,880
[SPEAKER_02] u svojim ulogama.

1447
01:30:04,880 --> 01:30:07,380
[SPEAKER_02] Jedna od naj, za djelicu,

1448
01:30:07,380 --> 01:30:09,619
[SPEAKER_02] od najvažnijih stvari od kojih oni uče

1449
01:30:09,619 --> 01:30:11,319
[SPEAKER_02] kako se mama i tata vola.

1450
01:30:11,319 --> 01:30:17,100
[SPEAKER_02] Ne, ono, škola, matematika, fizika, kemijan.

1451
01:30:17,100 --> 01:30:19,460
[SPEAKER_02] Stvari koje njih definiraju kao osobe

1452
01:30:19,460 --> 01:30:21,359
[SPEAKER_02] za život cijeli je kako mama voli

1453
01:30:21,359 --> 01:30:23,220
[SPEAKER_02] tato i kako tata voli mamu.

1454
01:30:23,220 --> 01:30:24,239
[SPEAKER_02] To su najvažnije stvari.

1455
01:30:24,239 --> 01:30:26,720
[SPEAKER_02] Jer se onda on uči svom identitetu.

1456
01:30:26,720 --> 01:30:29,380
[SPEAKER_02] Ako imam sina, on gleda što kakav se

1457
01:30:29,380 --> 01:30:31,380
[SPEAKER_02] nekakav muškarac, to je jedna moja uloga.

1458
01:30:31,380 --> 01:30:33,859
[SPEAKER_02] Kako se odnosi sam sa sobom, sa svom spolnošću,

1459
01:30:33,859 --> 01:30:35,220
[SPEAKER_02] kako upravljam novcima,

1460
01:30:35,220 --> 01:30:38,039
[SPEAKER_02] kako donosim odluke, kako delegiram,

1461
01:30:38,840 --> 01:30:40,960
[SPEAKER_02] kako discipliniram, a onda kako ja ljubim

1462
01:30:40,960 --> 01:30:41,840
[SPEAKER_02] drugu ženu.

1463
01:30:41,840 --> 01:30:43,500
[SPEAKER_02] Kako ljubim njih kao djecu.

1464
01:30:43,500 --> 01:30:46,319
[SPEAKER_02] Jedna je uloga biti muž, jedna je uloga biti otac.

1465
01:30:46,319 --> 01:30:48,140
[SPEAKER_02] Jedna je uloga biti poslodavac,

1466
01:30:48,140 --> 01:30:50,640
[SPEAKER_02] jer sam imam svoj obrat.

1467
01:30:50,640 --> 01:30:52,739
[SPEAKER_02] Kako se odnosim prema drugim ljudima,

1468
01:30:52,739 --> 01:30:55,079
[SPEAKER_02] i onda on gleda, i on gleda kako ja to učim.

1469
01:30:55,079 --> 01:30:57,760
[SPEAKER_02] I onda se, 90% toga,

1470
01:30:57,760 --> 01:30:58,920
[SPEAKER_02] on uči u pijanje.

1471
01:30:58,920 --> 01:31:00,439
[SPEAKER_02] On samo to što je smeno,

1472
01:31:00,439 --> 01:31:02,880
[SPEAKER_02] što sam prišao u ovom životu, njega to oblikuje.

1473
01:31:03,680 --> 01:31:05,560
[SPEAKER_02] Mi sam njega učio, sam svaki dana mu pričao,

1474
01:31:05,560 --> 01:31:06,199
[SPEAKER_02] i pametovo.

1475
01:31:06,199 --> 01:31:09,720
[SPEAKER_02] Kako tako, najmanje ljudi tako nešto uči.

1476
01:31:09,720 --> 01:31:11,699
[SPEAKER_02] Naša djeca uče u pijanjem i gledanjem.

1477
01:31:11,699 --> 01:31:14,220
[SPEAKER_02] Moja čer nas gleda,

1478
01:31:14,220 --> 01:31:16,180
[SPEAKER_02] i kad mi mi ne znamo da nas gleda.

1479
01:31:16,460 --> 01:31:18,880
[SPEAKER_02] Ja znamo, ona je toliko regla zastrašujući komentara,

1480
01:31:18,880 --> 01:31:19,779
[SPEAKER_02] da se misli,

1481
01:31:19,779 --> 01:31:21,619
[SPEAKER_02] Isu se Bože, kako ti to gledaš?

1482
01:31:21,619 --> 01:31:23,479
[SPEAKER_02] Ona djeca osjećaju,

1483
01:31:23,479 --> 01:31:25,779
[SPEAKER_02] imaju brutalnu onaku pronicljivost,

1484
01:31:25,779 --> 01:31:28,640
[SPEAKER_02] onako kužaj stvari koje ne možeš vjerovat da kužaj.

1485
01:31:28,640 --> 01:31:30,340
[SPEAKER_02] Mi umanjujemo njihov potencijal.

1486
01:31:30,340 --> 01:31:31,939
[SPEAKER_01] Najbolji su promotorači.

1487
01:31:31,939 --> 01:31:32,659
[SPEAKER_02] Najbolji.

1488
01:31:32,659 --> 01:31:33,939
[SPEAKER_02] A najbolji tumači.

1489
01:31:33,939 --> 01:31:35,960
[SPEAKER_02] I onda kad moja čer nešto kaže

1490
01:31:35,960 --> 01:31:37,960
[SPEAKER_02] što mi bude najbolja konstruktivna kritika,

1491
01:31:37,960 --> 01:31:39,979
[SPEAKER_02] ja kažem, ako ti to ču, vidiš,

1492
01:31:39,979 --> 01:31:41,340
[SPEAKER_02] ako ti to razumiješ,

1493
01:31:41,340 --> 01:31:42,680
[SPEAKER_02] onda nešto treba mijenjati,

1494
01:31:43,020 --> 01:31:44,140
[SPEAKER_02] ako ti to vidiš.

1495
01:31:44,140 --> 01:31:46,840
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da, djeca su najbolji filter

1496
01:31:46,840 --> 01:31:48,479
[SPEAKER_02] i najbolji kritičar poslije žene.

1497
01:31:48,479 --> 01:31:50,899
[SPEAKER_02] Naravno, žena je najbolji kritičar

1498
01:31:50,899 --> 01:31:52,319
[SPEAKER_02] koji postoji za nas muževe,

1499
01:31:52,319 --> 01:31:53,800
[SPEAKER_02] ali djeca su brutalni.

1500
01:31:53,800 --> 01:31:55,600
[SPEAKER_02] Kad bi bolje slušali našu djecu

1501
01:31:55,600 --> 01:31:57,119
[SPEAKER_02] i kad bi više sudjelovali

1502
01:31:57,119 --> 01:31:58,420
[SPEAKER_02] i njih tražili da pričaju s nama,

1503
01:31:58,420 --> 01:32:00,760
[SPEAKER_02] onda bi vidjeli koje stvari su stvarno važne.

1504
01:32:00,760 --> 01:32:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, zapravo poruka današnjeg podcasta je

1505
01:32:03,380 --> 01:32:05,220
[SPEAKER_00] očevi i majke, ljubite svoju djecu,

1506
01:32:05,220 --> 01:32:07,640
[SPEAKER_00] usagljujte im prave vrijednosti,

1507
01:32:07,640 --> 01:32:10,260
[SPEAKER_00] da imaju onu uspravnicu u životu

1508
01:32:10,260 --> 01:32:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] u kojoj se mogu uzdati, zvrne?

1509
01:32:12,460 --> 01:32:13,439
[SPEAKER_02] Ali, prosište.

1510
01:32:13,439 --> 01:32:15,420
[SPEAKER_02] Dajte, dajte, izlovite.

1511
01:32:15,420 --> 01:32:19,000
[SPEAKER_02] Gdje je problem u ovome društvu gdje sad imamo?

1512
01:32:19,000 --> 01:32:22,140
[SPEAKER_02] Ako neko nije primio ljubav i vrijednost,

1513
01:32:22,140 --> 01:32:24,199
[SPEAKER_02] u ovom slučaju mi kažemo

1514
01:32:24,199 --> 01:32:25,640
[SPEAKER_02] očevi i majke ljubite,

1515
01:32:25,640 --> 01:32:27,399
[SPEAKER_02] a oni sami to nisu primiti.

1516
01:32:27,399 --> 01:32:29,119
[SPEAKER_02] Prvo, jako teško će to napravi.

1517
01:32:29,119 --> 01:32:31,600
[SPEAKER_02] I sad, to je izazov da generacije

1518
01:32:31,600 --> 01:32:33,859
[SPEAKER_02] koji su ranjene, a imaju na preveć djecu

1519
01:32:33,859 --> 01:32:35,340
[SPEAKER_02] ili trebaju dobiti tijek djecu

1520
01:32:35,340 --> 01:32:36,420
[SPEAKER_02] ili se razmišlja o tome,

1521
01:32:36,420 --> 01:32:38,699
[SPEAKER_02] oni moraju istovremeno i prolazi

1522
01:32:38,699 --> 01:32:40,539
[SPEAKER_02] s put svog nutarnog isceljenja

1523
01:32:40,539 --> 01:32:41,560
[SPEAKER_02] i osnaženja

1524
01:32:41,560 --> 01:32:44,920
[SPEAKER_02] i istovremeno dati o nekom drugom.

1525
01:32:44,920 --> 01:32:46,100
[SPEAKER_02] Sve dopisamo, ali ono.

1526
01:32:46,100 --> 01:32:48,039
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim, ne može dati nešto što nisi primio.

1527
01:32:48,039 --> 01:32:48,439
[SPEAKER_02] Točno.

1528
01:32:48,479 --> 01:32:49,539
[SPEAKER_02] Ako ne jaš tišće eura,

1529
01:32:49,539 --> 01:32:50,399
[SPEAKER_02] ne može ih ni dati.

1530
01:32:50,399 --> 01:32:50,720
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

1531
01:32:50,720 --> 01:32:54,000
[SPEAKER_02] Tako isto sa, naprijedno vrijednosti.

1532
01:32:54,000 --> 01:32:55,560
[SPEAKER_02] Ako ti ne jaš u duboku usređenu

1533
01:32:55,560 --> 01:32:56,279
[SPEAKER_02] osjećaj vrijednosti,

1534
01:32:56,279 --> 01:32:57,539
[SPEAKER_02] ti može pričati koko hoće,

1535
01:32:57,539 --> 01:32:59,439
[SPEAKER_02] ali tvoje djeto upije tvoju bezvrijednost.

1536
01:32:59,439 --> 01:33:01,859
[SPEAKER_02] Ono osjeća stvari na dubljoj razini.

1537
01:33:01,859 --> 01:33:03,300
[SPEAKER_02] I onda tvoje djete,

1538
01:33:03,300 --> 01:33:04,239
[SPEAKER_02] ti može pričati,

1539
01:33:04,239 --> 01:33:05,800
[SPEAKER_02] ne znam, to je isto kod nekog kaže,

1540
01:33:05,800 --> 01:33:07,199
[SPEAKER_02] pušenje štedno, a puši.

1541
01:33:07,199 --> 01:33:09,180
[SPEAKER_02] A tvoje djete te neće nikad pušenje.

1542
01:33:09,180 --> 01:33:10,539
[SPEAKER_02] Rozvlašiti primjer najbolji.

1543
01:33:10,539 --> 01:33:12,039
[SPEAKER_02] I sad, ako ti želiš djeci

1544
01:33:12,039 --> 01:33:13,600
[SPEAKER_02] govoriti o tome koliko vrijede

1545
01:33:13,600 --> 01:33:15,560
[SPEAKER_02] i ići, ne znam, u njima uljevat ljubav,

1546
01:33:15,560 --> 01:33:17,739
[SPEAKER_02] a ti se ošćaš nevoljeno, odbačeno,

1547
01:33:17,739 --> 01:33:20,319
[SPEAKER_02] neštabilnost, emotivnost,

1548
01:33:20,319 --> 01:33:22,699
[SPEAKER_02] ono, rasturan, razvanjan,

1549
01:33:22,699 --> 01:33:24,699
[SPEAKER_02] onda ti to ne možeš ni kvalitetno da zato.

1550
01:33:24,699 --> 01:33:27,260
[SPEAKER_02] Zato uvijek izazov da ti moraš to prijaviti.

1551
01:33:27,260 --> 01:33:28,979
[SPEAKER_02] Bez uzira koga godina imaš.

1552
01:33:28,979 --> 01:33:30,560
[SPEAKER_02] Ljudi dožive unutarnje isjeljenje

1553
01:33:30,560 --> 01:33:31,880
[SPEAKER_02] sa 80 godina.

1554
01:33:31,880 --> 01:33:33,380
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, godine Bogu nisu prepreki

1555
01:33:33,380 --> 01:33:34,939
[SPEAKER_02] ili čovjeku, ajmo reći,

1556
01:33:34,939 --> 01:33:38,060
[SPEAKER_02] godine mu nisu prepreka

1557
01:33:38,060 --> 01:33:40,760
[SPEAKER_02] da on napravi nešto dobro za sebe,

1558
01:33:40,760 --> 01:33:42,520
[SPEAKER_02] da on primi nešto, da promijeni se.

1559
01:33:42,520 --> 01:33:44,319
[SPEAKER_02] Mene su uvijek žicirale

1560
01:33:44,319 --> 01:33:45,460
[SPEAKER_02] onaj izjave kad kaže

1561
01:33:45,460 --> 01:33:47,220
[SPEAKER_02] da se čovjek ne mijenja nikad.

1562
01:33:47,220 --> 01:33:49,560
[SPEAKER_02] To je to dalna istina.

1563
01:33:49,560 --> 01:33:51,319
[SPEAKER_02] Čovjek je sposoban se promijeniti,

1564
01:33:51,319 --> 01:33:52,979
[SPEAKER_02] čovjek je sposoban doživiti isjeljenje,

1565
01:33:52,979 --> 01:33:54,199
[SPEAKER_02] oslobođenje, uvijek.

1566
01:33:54,199 --> 01:33:55,979
[SPEAKER_02] I htjel bih sa mna dovezati,

1567
01:33:55,979 --> 01:33:57,560
[SPEAKER_02] šta bi bilo to ne reći,

1568
01:33:57,560 --> 01:33:58,840
[SPEAKER_02] kad on priča

1569
01:33:58,840 --> 01:34:02,060
[SPEAKER_02] odgovoru kako promijeniti

1570
01:34:02,060 --> 01:34:03,260
[SPEAKER_02] možemo današnje društvo.

1571
01:34:03,260 --> 01:34:05,920
[SPEAKER_02] Ja želim to iz svoje situacije reći.

1572
01:34:06,180 --> 01:34:08,399
[SPEAKER_02] Vjerujem da će dobar dio vjernika tu slušati,

1573
01:34:08,399 --> 01:34:09,619
[SPEAKER_02] nadam se možda i neki

1574
01:34:09,619 --> 01:34:13,460
[SPEAKER_02] iz crkvenih hierarhijskih ovih dijelova.

1575
01:34:13,460 --> 01:34:16,739
[SPEAKER_02] Ja mislim i želio bi dati jednu konstruktivnu kritiku crp.

1576
01:34:16,739 --> 01:34:19,020
[SPEAKER_02] Crkva bi trebala biti nukleos,

1577
01:34:19,020 --> 01:34:20,340
[SPEAKER_02] ona je najveća sila,

1578
01:34:20,340 --> 01:34:22,159
[SPEAKER_02] jer ona ima duha svetog.

1579
01:34:22,159 --> 01:34:23,579
[SPEAKER_02] Duha sveti je dinamis,

1580
01:34:23,579 --> 01:34:25,020
[SPEAKER_02] on je moćan, on je silan.

1581
01:34:25,020 --> 01:34:27,100
[SPEAKER_02] To je treća božanska osoba

1582
01:34:27,100 --> 01:34:28,739
[SPEAKER_02] koja je lepdila nadvodana,

1583
01:34:28,739 --> 01:34:30,180
[SPEAKER_02] stvarala, oblikovala svijet

1584
01:34:30,180 --> 01:34:31,340
[SPEAKER_02] i oblikovala čovjeka.

1585
01:34:31,340 --> 01:34:33,180
[SPEAKER_02] I mi koji imamo duha svetog,

1586
01:34:33,239 --> 01:34:35,220
[SPEAKER_02] mi bi trebali biti ljudi koji donose promijenu.

1587
01:34:35,220 --> 01:34:37,340
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ne očekujem od političara

1588
01:34:37,340 --> 01:34:38,220
[SPEAKER_02] da će promijenit vas.

1589
01:34:38,220 --> 01:34:40,479
[SPEAKER_02] Ne očekujem od znanstvenika,

1590
01:34:40,479 --> 01:34:40,979
[SPEAKER_02] od testa.

1591
